Implemented the V03 fixes and wrote the required report at `.review-slices/V03.fix.md`.

Changed Anvil scoped files for:

- reset baseline restoration
- dump/load round-trip compatibility
- stop impersonation account matching
- positional `anvil_dropTransaction` hash handling
- `anvil_setStorageAt` returning `true`
- related request/result typing

I did not run tests or build commands, per the slice constraints.
